java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>

uk.co.terminological.rjava.types.RVector<RFactor>
uk.co.terminological.rjava.types.RFactorVector
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<RFactor>, Collection<RFactor>, List<RFactor>, RandomAccess, RObject
public class RFactorVector extends RVector<RFactor>
A Java wrapper for factors. R Factors can be mapped to java enumeration by the RConverter class. Factory methods are in RVector.
